about.description: django-cruds-adminlte is simple drop-in django app that creates CRUD (Create, read, update and delete) views for existing models and apps.
about.summary: django-cruds is simple drop-in django app that creates CRUD for faster prototyping

name: django-cruds-adminlte
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "django-cruds-adminlte" %}
{% set version = "0.0.12" %}
{% set sha256 = "5e278f575ac5ff3069856eec106ce30b454eb7cf8a4d788be9a6600f12765013" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - django-crispy-forms

test:
  imports:
    - cruds_adminlte
    - cruds_adminlte.templatetags

about:
  home: https://github.com/oscarmlage/django-cruds-adminlte
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'django-cruds is simple drop-in django app that creates CRUD for faster prototyping'
  description: 
    django-cruds-adminlte is simple drop-in django app that creates CRUD (Create, read, update 
    and delete) views for existing models and apps.
  doc_url: http://django-cruds-adminlte.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/oscarmlage/django-cruds-adminlte

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cshaley
    - sannykr
